headline: Elevance Health (ELV): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: Shareholders of Elevance Health would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 24.6% and now trades at $308.66. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
